column1: The file contains a comparison of ANN model with a GC-based method for several ionic liquids reported in the article Y. Chen, Y. Cai, K. Thomsen, G. M. Kontogeorgis, J. M. Woodley, A group contribution-based prediction method for the electrical conductivity of ionic liquids, Fluid Phase Equilibria (2020) 112462.
We have reported this comparison in the article entitled 'Developing Machine Learning Models for Ionic Conductivity of Imidazolium-Based Ionic Liquids'
Authors: Pratik Dhakal and Jindal K. Shah
